  <brief_title>The Influence of Inspiratory Muscular Training (IMT) on Diaphragmatic Mobility in Morbidly Obese</brief_title>
  <official_title>The Influence of Inspiratory Muscular Training on Diaphragmatic Mobility, Lung Function and Quality of Life in Obese Individuals</official_title>
  <sponsors>
